[I] Tools for use with the s390 Linux kernel and device drivers

[T] The s390-tools package contains the source tree of a set of user space
[T] utilities for use with the s390 Linux kernel and device drivers.

[U] https://github.com/ibm-s390-linux/s390-tools/

[A] International Business Machines (IBM)
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS
[R] + s390x

[L] MIT
[V] 2.42.1

[D] 3661ea575cbf2584759f4ebcc7b8065e8ca9a6bf614c4df5b3aefbf5 s390-tools-2.42.1.tar.gz https://github.com/ibm-s390-linux/s390-tools/archive/v2.42.1/

var_append makeopt ' ' OBJCOPY=$OBJCOPY
var_append makeopt ' ' "HAVE_SNMP=0 HAVE_FUSE=0 HAVE_CARGO=0"
var_append makeinstopt ' ' "HAVE_SNMP=0 HAVE_FUSE=0 HAVE_CARGO=0"
var_append GCC_WRAPPER_INSERT ' ' -Os
